          "provision_label_raw": "21.2",
          "text": "MR-2 ZONE REQUIREMENTS In any MR-2 Zone, no development permit shall be issued except in conformity with the following: Minimum Lot Area 4,000 square feet (371.6 m2) Minimum Frontage 40 feet (12.2 m) Minimum Front or Flankage Yard 20 feet (6.1 m) Minimum Side Yard 8 feet (2.4 m)",
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
